{"tid":1824410,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「土耳其皇帝」哈根蘇古不能回國，只好美國開Uber","createTime":"2020-01-14T11:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T21:38:36.000Z","uid":228995,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80bcd53e99e982db4ee94e3e8a71aba018d91d46","tid":1824410,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"//還記得「土耳其皇帝」哈根蘇古（Hakan Sukur）嗎？這位土耳其名宿因為得罪獨裁者埃多安，被迫流亡美國，既不能與家人相見，財產亦被政府凍結。現在只能在華盛頓開Uber維生。他控訴埃多安：「他把我的一切都剝奪了」。<br />\n<br />\n哈根蘇古是2002年世界盃土耳其取得季軍的功臣，球員生涯曾效力加拉塔沙雷、國際米蘭、帕爾馬、布力般流浪等球會，更是加拉塔沙雷千禧年奪取歐洲足協盃冠軍的功臣。哈根蘇古在退役後從政，一度加入埃多安的正義與發展黨（英文簡稱AKP），但在2013年因為政見不合而脫黨。自此後埃多安把他視為政權敵人，並大力打壓。他透露，自己曾在加州經營咖啡店，但屢遭破壞，㺺在靠賣書和開Uber維持收入。蘇古描述，破壞者播放著AKP宣揚的音樂。而在美國跟蘇古合照過的土耳其學生，更因此被囚14個月。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sportsyeah.hk/2020/01/14/%e5%be%97%e7%bd%aa%e5%9f%83%e5%a4%9a%e5%ae%89%e8%a2%ab%e8%bf%ab%e6%b5%81%e4%ba%a1%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b-%e5%93%88%e6%a0%b9%e8%98%87%e5%8f%a4%e9%96%8buber%e7%b6%ad%e7%94%9f-%ef%bd%9c-%e9%ab%94%e5%98%a2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportsyeah.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F14%2F%25e5%25be%2597%25e7%25bd%25aa%25e5%259f%2583%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%25ae%2589%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e8%25bf%25ab%25e6%25b5%2581%25e4%25ba%25a1%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b-%25e5%2593%2588%25e6%25a0%25b9%25e8%2598%2587%25e5%258f%25a4%25e9%2596%258buber%25e7%25b6%25ad%25e7%2594%259f-%25ef%25bd%259c-%25e9%25ab%2594%25e5%2598%25a2%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=aed019aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sportsyeah.hk/2020/01/14/%e5%be%97%e7%bd%aa%e5%9f%83%e5%a4%9a%e5%ae%89%e8%a2%ab%e8%bf%ab%e6%b5%81%e4%ba%a1%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b-%e5%93%88%e6%a0%b9%e8%98%87%e5%8f%a4%e9%96%8buber%e7%b6%ad%e7%94%9f-%ef%bd%9c-%e9%ab%94%e5%98%a2/</a><br />\n<br />\n不如過香港踢港超？<br />\n<br />\n應該夠做"},{"pid":"7d26b1f539e61aa3cfbdf749eddb981fd8d2f256","tid":1824410,"uid":121058,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"火雞國仲想加入歐盟<br />\n死番去同支那一齊柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9c61579a8f2ab8c7be744ae9fe90adc252ee64","tid":1824410,"uid":10199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"海外戶口既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c3d5eadacc492aa2664fd53ad7f453e424ffba","tid":1824410,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:38:36.000Z","msg":"香港都不遑多讓"}]}